# Per-run randomized artifacts (suffixed with the random run id) are
# regenerated every time the M2 worker round-trip test executes; the
# committed copies are the canonical job-0023 acceptance evidence.
#
# When the suite is re-run, new files appear here with a fresh random
# suffix — those are local-only by default. Re-record canonical evidence
# by overwriting the tracked files explicitly.
execute-stderr-*.log
execute-stdout-*.json
mutated-*.qgs
worker-notify-*.json
!execute-stderr-49c6c439.log
!execute-stdout-49c6c439.json
!mutated-49c6c439.qgs
!worker-notify-49c6c439.json
